snippet.title: The Sims 4 Backyard Stuff: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Create a casual backyard space for your Sims to kick back and cool off with The Sims 4 Backyard Stuff.
 
Learn more about this Stuff Pack: http://x.ea.com/8874
 
Attempt crazy tricks on the lawn water slide or chill out with a glass of lemonade. Decorate the backyard with colorful new objects and outfit your Sims in laid-back fashion.
